name: AF_Cluster
description: Predict multiple protein conformations using sequence clustering and AlphaFold2.

name: Final-Thesis-Code
description: This repository contains data processing, threshold detection, and clustering analysis tools for studying pedestrian movement patterns in high-density rushing scenarios across multiple experiments. It includes scripts for data cleaning, segmentation, and clustering using DBSCAN and hierarchical methods.

name: AI-Based-Cache-System-for-Optimizing-Hotel-Price-API-Calls
description: This project aims to optimize search engine API calls for hotel prices by using an AI-based caching system. The system determines the optimal Time to Live (TTL) for cached records based on dynamically calculated `changing_price_rate` values for each vendor and hotel.

name: TCS-Stock-Price-Prediction
description: This project aims to predict the stock prices of Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) using a combination of Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks, K-Means Clustering, and Logistic Regression. The system integrates these techniques to analyze historical stock price data and forecast future trends, enabling better investment decisions.

name: Coffee-Sales-Prediction
description: This project aims to predict coffee sales using different machine learning models: Support Vector Machine (SVM) Regression, Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) neural network, Support Vector Machine (SVM) Classification, and K-Means Clustering.

name: Starbucks-data-analysis-customer-segmentation
description: This project focuses on analyzing and segmenting Starbucks customers to understand their behavior and preferences. The goal is to create meaningful customer segments using clustering techniques and to visualize customer profiles based on various demographic and interaction data.

name: Music-Recommendation-System
description: Utilized k-means clustering to identify patterns, observing that similar songs and genres cluster together

name: k8s_resource_monitor
description: A CLI tool for monitoring Kubernetes resources and autoscaling

name: User_Analysis_and_Engagement
description: Advanced workflows for user behavior and engagement analysis. Features in-depth EDA, visualization techniques, and statistical methods to uncover insights from user interaction data. Aimed at providing a technical understanding of engagement trends for data-driven decision-making.
